org.afplib.afplib

Interface FNORG

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, Triplet
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    FNORGImpl

    public interface FNORG
extends Triplet
    A representation of the model object 'FNORG'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Reserved
    • Char Rot
    • Max BOset
    • Max Char Inc
    • Sp Char Inc
    • Max BExt
    • Ornt Flgs
    • Reserved2
    • Em Sp Inc
    • Reserved3
    • Fig Sp Inc
    • Nom Char Inc
    • Def BInc
    • Min ASp

    See Also:
    AfplibPackage.getFNORG()
